(275, '_transient_Travelpayouts_TPRssNewEN', 'a:1:{s:4:\"data\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:60:\"Travelpayouts Blog – Travel affiliates – Travel Partners\";s:4:\"link\";s:33:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\";s:11:\"description\";s:40:\"Travelpayouts - Complete travel solution\";s:13:\"lastBuildDate\";s:31:\"Tue, 13 Feb 2018 13:03:38 +0000\";s:8:\"language\";s:5:\"en-US\";s:9:\"generator\";s:30:\"https://wordpress.org/?v=4.9.3\";s:4:\"item\";a:10:{i:0;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:59:\"The best practices of the successful Booking.com affiliates\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TravelpayoutsBlog/~3/no0oropM8NA/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:68:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/booking-com-best-practice/#respond\";s:7:\"pubDate\";s:31:\"Mon, 12 Feb 2018 08:56:23 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";s:14:\"Cases and tips\";s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/?p=1279\";s:11:\"description\";s:1123:\"<div>\n	<a href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/booking-com-best-practice/\"><img title=\"The best practices of the successful Booking.com affiliates\" src=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2016/04/Make_money_with_hotel_affiliate_program_2-200x105.png\" alt=\"The best practices of the successful Booking.com affiliates\" width=\"200\" height=\"105\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></a>\n	</div>\n<p>	Last year, Travelpayouts held the very first travel affiliate event — Travelpayouts Affiliate Summit. One of the speakers — Ekaterina Rakova (Booking.com), presented the best practices of the successful affiliates. This information is extremely valuable for webmasters who want to know about the people making thousands of dollars monthly on online travel market and how [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/booking-com-best-practice/\">The best practices of the successful Booking.com affiliates</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\">Travelpayouts Blog - Travel affiliates - Travel Partners</a>.</p>\n\";}i:1;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:64:\"Sell Kiwitaxi transfers and get 50% of advertiser’s commission\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TravelpayoutsBlog/~3/NDTL87frW5o/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:61:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/kiwitaxi-transfers/#respond\";s:7:\"pubDate\";s:31:\"Fri, 09 Feb 2018 09:09:00 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";s:14:\"Cases and tips\";s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/?p=1363\";s:11:\"description\";s:1017:\"<div>\n	<a href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/kiwitaxi-transfers/\"><img title=\"kiwitaxi-service-for-clients\" src=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/02/kiwitaxi-service-for-clients-200x98.png\" alt=\"kiwitaxi-service-for-clients\" width=\"200\" height=\"98\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></a>\n	</div>\n<p>	Kiwitaxi is an international system for booking tourist transfers. Kiwitaxi site is available in 5 languages. Our carriers perform the transfers in more than 738 airports in 99 countries. A car park range includes more than 10 car classes from economy sedans and hatchbacks to 19-seat minibuses. The cars are functional, passed a technical inspection [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/kiwitaxi-transfers/\">Sell Kiwitaxi transfers and get 50% of advertiser&#8217;s commission</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\">Travelpayouts Blog - Travel affiliates - Travel Partners</a>.</p>\n\";}i:2;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:47:\"Collecting your Cases for a Travelpayouts bonus\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TravelpayoutsBlog/~3/ym62V6CWdDM/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:76:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/collect-cases-travelpayouts-bonus/#respond\";s:7:\"pubDate\";s:31:\"Wed, 07 Feb 2018 08:31:35 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";s:14:\"Cases and tips\";s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/?p=1361\";s:11:\"description\";s:1036:\"<div>\n	<a href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/collect-cases-travelpayouts-bonus/\"><img title=\"Collecting your Cases for a Travelpayouts bonus\" src=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2016/11/cases-wanted-200x105.png\" alt=\"Collecting your Cases for a Travelpayouts bonus\" width=\"200\" height=\"105\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></a>\n	</div>\n<p>	Dear friends, we are continuing a column in our blog called Our Partners&#8217; Cases. It is high time you shared your success story, motivated your colleagues and received a Travelpayouts bonus. Briefly and to the Point If you believe that sharing your experience will be helpful for other webmasters, we look forward to receiving your [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/collect-cases-travelpayouts-bonus/\">Collecting your Cases for a Travelpayouts bonus</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\">Travelpayouts Blog - Travel affiliates - Travel Partners</a>.</p>\n\";}i:3;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:50:\"Travelpayouts promo codes for registration in 2018\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TravelpayoutsBlog/~3/ZSplFTqh4x8/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:71:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/promo-codes-for-registration/#respond\";s:7:\"pubDate\";s:31:\"Tue, 06 Feb 2018 09:15:36 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";s:13:\"Uncategorized\";s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/?p=1350\";s:11:\"description\";s:973:\"<div>\n	<a href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/promo-codes-for-registration/\"><img title=\"zamenit\" src=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/02/zamenit-200x129.jpg\" alt=\"Travelpayouts promo codes for registration in 2018\" width=\"200\" height=\"129\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></a>\n	</div>\n<p>	The promo codes for registration in Travelpayouts are special codes that allow you to get a commission rising to 90%. Usually, the commission increase is relevant for a limited period, from 1 month to 3 months, depending on the Travelpayouts code that you used during the registration. On this page, you will learn how the [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/promo-codes-for-registration/\">Travelpayouts promo codes for registration in 2018</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\">Travelpayouts Blog - Travel affiliates - Travel Partners</a>.</p>\n\";}i:4;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:71:\"12Go Asia — earn on booking flights, buses, ferries and train tickets\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TravelpayoutsBlog/~3/KG76fI4AbhI/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:52:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/12go-asia/#respond\";s:7:\"pubDate\";s:31:\"Tue, 30 Jan 2018 10:09:00 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";s:14:\"Cases and tips\";s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/?p=1326\";s:11:\"description\";s:1050:\"<div>\n	<a href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/12go-asia/\"><img title=\"12Go Asia — earn on booking flights, buses, ferries and train tickets\" src=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/12go-asia.png\" alt=\"12Go Asia — earn on booking flights, buses, ferries and train tickets\" width=\"200\" height=\"105\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></a>\n	</div>\n<p>	12Go Asia is a Bangkok based OTA (Online Travel Agency) providing a powerful booking system for multimodal transportation and day trips around Southeast Asia currently expanding our coverage to other parts of Asia and worldwide. We help travellers (B2C) and companies (B2B) to book flights, bus, van, ferry, train tickets and transfers at the touch [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/12go-asia/\">12Go Asia — earn on booking flights, buses, ferries and train tickets</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\">Travelpayouts Blog - Travel affiliates - Travel Partners</a>.</p>\n\";}i:5;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:67:\"Weatlas.com — earn on sightseeings and transfers around the world\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TravelpayoutsBlog/~3/4UVheqVzvas/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:77:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/earn-on-sightseeings-and-transfers/#respond\";s:7:\"pubDate\";s:31:\"Thu, 25 Jan 2018 09:50:23 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";s:14:\"Cases and tips\";s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/?p=1321\";s:11:\"description\";s:1112:\"<div>\n	<a href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/earn-on-sightseeings-and-transfers/\"><img title=\"Weatlas.com — earn on sightseeings and transfers around the world\" src=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/weatlas-case.png\" alt=\"Weatlas.com — earn on sightseeings and transfers around the world\" width=\"200\" height=\"104\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></a>\n	</div>\n<p>	Weatlas.com is a Russian online service (hub) for booking sightseeings and transfers around the world, focused mainly on the Russian-speaking customers. However, the site has its English version and almost all our guides and drivers speak Russian and English. Weatlas is: 4 200+ sightseeings and entertainment tickets 60 000+ transfers worldwide great service from 2012 [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/earn-on-sightseeings-and-transfers/\">Weatlas.com — earn on sightseeings and transfers around the world</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\">Travelpayouts Blog - Travel affiliates - Travel Partners</a>.</p>\n\";}i:6;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:72:\"Travelpayouts at the Affiliate Summit West 2018 in Las Vegas: how it was\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TravelpayoutsBlog/~3/a2Qp5mAt5co/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:80:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/las-vegas-affiliate-summit-west-2018/#comments\";s:7:\"pubDate\";s:31:\"Mon, 22 Jan 2018 09:06:09 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";a:3:{i:0;s:6:\"Events\";i:1;s:5:\"event\";i:2;s:5:\"vegas\";}s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/?p=1308\";s:11:\"description\";s:1094:\"<div>\n	<a href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/las-vegas-affiliate-summit-west-2018/\"><img title=\"Travelpayouts at the Affiliate Summit West 2018 in Las Vegas: how it was\" src=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/01/team-200x133.jpg\" alt=\"Travelpayouts at the Affiliate Summit West 2018 in Las Vegas: how it was\" width=\"200\" height=\"133\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></a>\n	</div>\n<p>	In early January, the main event on the affiliate-market: Affiliate Summit West 2018 was held in Las Vegas. The advanced experience from 2016 left no doubts for us to partake the next time, so the Travelpayouts team visited the United States again. Thanks to everyone who stopped by our stand, we are always glad to meet [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/las-vegas-affiliate-summit-west-2018/\">Travelpayouts at the Affiliate Summit West 2018 in Las Vegas: how it was</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\">Travelpayouts Blog - Travel affiliates - Travel Partners</a>.</p>\n\";}i:7;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:42:\"Arabic and Hebrew languages in White Label\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TravelpayoutsBlog/~3/E0NSnYyg86I/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:71:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/arabic-language-white-label/#comments\";s:7:\"pubDate\";s:31:\"Fri, 19 Jan 2018 09:14:31 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";s:4:\"News\";s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/?p=1302\";s:11:\"description\";s:966:\"<div>\n	<a href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/arabic-language-white-label/\"><img title=\"Arabic language in White Label\" src=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/01/arabic-language-white-label-200x105.png\" alt=\"Arabic language in White Label\" width=\"200\" height=\"105\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></a>\n	</div>\n<p>	We have great news for our Arabic-speaking partners — our White Label supports Arabic language (Hebrew as well). You can check it out in your Travelpayouts account. In case you’ve never used our WL or don’t know how to set it up — take a look at our help article here. Try our new White Label! [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/arabic-language-white-label/\">Arabic and Hebrew languages in White Label</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\">Travelpayouts Blog - Travel affiliates - Travel Partners</a>.</p>\n\";}i:8;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:25:\"Mobile App in White Label\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TravelpayoutsBlog/~3/qcrsQpvu9UM/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:66:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/mobile-app-white-label/#comments\";s:7:\"pubDate\";s:31:\"Thu, 18 Jan 2018 10:31:01 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";s:14:\"Cases and tips\";s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/?p=1293\";s:11:\"description\";s:900:\"<div>\n	<a href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/mobile-app-white-label/\"><img title=\"Mobile App in White Label\" src=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/mobile-app-white-label.png\" alt=\"Mobile App in White Label\" width=\"200\" height=\"105\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></a>\n	</div>\n<p>	Mobile app feature allows your visitors to download mobile app for iOS with your color settings, logo, name, etc. All sales performed using this app will enter in your account. How it works The mechanism is simple, since we have created a blank app for iOS and uploaded it to Apple Store. If it is [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/mobile-app-white-label/\">Mobile App in White Label</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\">Travelpayouts Blog - Travel affiliates - Travel Partners</a>.</p>\n\";}i:9;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:54:\"Turn 2018 FIFA World Cup into money with Travelpayouts\";s:4:\"link\";s:64:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TravelpayoutsBlog/~3/cs7l3Zf5cUw/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:53:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/world-cup/#comments\";s:7:\"pubDate\";s:31:\"Wed, 17 Jan 2018 08:54:46 +0000\";s:8:\"category\";s:14:\"Cases and tips\";s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/?p=1273\";s:11:\"description\";s:970:\"<div>\n	<a href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/world-cup/\"><img title=\"Turn 2018 FIFA World Cup into money with Travelpayouts\" src=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2018/01/fifa-world-cup-200x100.jpg\" alt=\"Turn 2018 FIFA World Cup into money with Travelpayouts\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" /></a>\n	</div>\n<p>	The 2018 FIFA World Cup will be held this summer in Russia and you can earn from it with Travelpayouts’ products. The championship is estimated to be very exciting and has already started attracting lots of fans from all over the world. Now is the right time to start to earn, do not miss out. [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en/world-cup/\">Turn 2018 FIFA World Cup into money with Travelpayouts</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.travelpayouts.com/en\">Travelpayouts Blog - Travel affiliates - Travel Partners</a>.</p>\n\";}}}}', 'no'),
